Button - sudoku中的类
Button class extends JButtons and creates the buttons for the Sudoku grid.
Button(int, boolean, int) - 类 的构造器sudoku.Button
Button constructor makes the buttons for the Sudoku grids.
ButtonPad - sudoku中的类
This class extends JButton to create the Sudoku game button pad.
ButtonPad(int) - 类 的构造器sudoku.ButtonPad
This constructor creates the button pad for the Sudoku game.
